                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17961130-37-defend347 t17961130-37-punish204"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
